title: Guitarist John Scofield on the Newport Jazz Festival
description:
In an interview taped backstage at the Newport Jazz Festival, guitarist John Scofield talks about his experiences at the festival from his time as a youth in Connecticut to his first appearance at Newport with Miles Davis.

This interview was taped backstage at the 2017 Newport Jazz Festival, where Scofield performed with the all-star band Hudson.  For more information about Scofield, visit www.johnscofield.com 

Interview by Irene Lee. Produced for JazzTimes by Lee Mergner. You can find more videos, plus news, features, reviews and lots more at www.jazztimes.com
